<div class="mx-auto" style="max-width: 920px;">
    <h1 class="mb-3">What’s new</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">
        A small changelog to show what’s been added and improved.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <div class="fw-semibold">2026-03-28</div>
        <ul class="text-muted mt-2">
            <li>Launched dedicated tool pages: <a href="/text-compare">Text compare</a>, <a href="/similarity-score">Similarity</a>, <a href="/json-viewer">JSON viewer</a>, <a href="/character-count">Character count</a>, <a href="/word-number-converter">Word ↔ Number</a>.</li>
